    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that it's a balance, but thats a bit of a cop out. if u had to pick one to be the absolute priority to prevent a collapse, which would it be? like, is it more \"responsible\" to pay down the debt first, or is it \"irresponsible\" to let people struggle just to balance a budget?",
